OL,3,CAuthor Hanif Kureishi on life-changing
OL,4,Cinjuries: My privacy is gone
OL,6,FHanif Kureishi has said his sense of
OL,7,Fself and privacy have been "completely
OL,8,Feradicated" after a fall on Boxing Day
OL,9,Fin Rome last year.
OL,11,FThe 69-year-old British author and
OL,12,Fplaywright spoke to BBC Radio 4's
OL,13,FToday programme as he guest edited the
OL,14,Fshow on Tuesday, a year after
OL,15,Fsustaining life-changing injuries.
OL,17,FAccording to the programme, Kureishi
OL,18,Fis still unable to use his arms or
OL,19,Flegs and has spent the last year in
OL,20,Ffive different hospitals.
